---
title: Creamy Lemon Dill Spaghetti & Shrimp with Blistered Grape Tomatoes & Chili Flakes
description: Love chicken alfredo? Then you’ll adore this dish! It’s a sophisticated riff on the classic with tons of flavor in every bite. There’s Italian-spiced chicken, juicy blistered tomatoes, chili flakes for a bit of heat, and al dente spaghetti. It’s all coated in a creamy, cheesy sauce brightened with the additions of lemon and dill.
